reviewText: As far as heinta goes, this is not standard, but there's something about the good story and great graphics that keeps me coming back. I will be buying the whole series.

As always, BB delivers. The story doesn't changes. And the quality of the drawings is still at its peak. Never the less there are abundant sex scenes and demonic  possessions nudity.
The downside of this DVD is that there aren't much male/female scenes but on the contrary countless female/shemales action. So that's the only negative remark.
If you are a previous viewer of the series it won't disappoint.
Wished I had more of the series to be complete. Awesome graphics and Dialog. The story gets better and better
